      <title>埃克森美孚收購先鋒公司需要 18 至 24 個月的時間才能全面推進</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-take-up-two-years-hit-stride-with-pioneer-purchase-2024-05-03/</link>
